{
  "stem": "21437.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think that somehow-- I don't know how with the walls-- but somehow the children in this particular town-- after all, this is-- this is where I lived.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they were somehow high achievers, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I think that the parents made sure that their Polish was fluent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So probably that's why they converse, many in Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think that like today, you let it all hang out and the parents discuss those things with the children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think then, it was just, you know, you were a child and you were loved and respected.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But things were just not explained to you, why you are doing certain things and what you are doing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just in front of you, and it should be done.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you didn't question it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was on the first floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a kitchen with a balcony.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a room next to it where-- I wouldn't want to call it servant, call her servant.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had a lady with us who only worked in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Didn't do anything else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we had--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Henia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The last one that we had was Henia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was Jewish, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it was a very large living room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then there was a passage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the right-hand side not far from the entrance was our bedroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the left-hand side was the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was another very big balcony leading out from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was what we call salon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like living-- living room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A very beautiful living room with those enormous windows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then there were three bedrooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One was a guest bathroom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My parents had a bedroom, of course, a large one.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
